profile:
A FULL-SERVICE MASONRY CONTRACTOR IN PETERBOROUGH, KAWARTHA LAKES AND THE SURROUNDING AREAS
When it comes to building and repairs for your property, you should only turn to a masonry contractor you can trust. At Sherren Masonry, we offer a complete spectrum of dependable masonry services, including installations, repairs, and restorations. We cater to residential and commercial projects in Peterborough, Kawartha Lakes and the surrounding areas.


We offer the following services for both interior and exterior projects:

   All masonry repairs and restorations

   Indoor and outdoor fireplaces

   Chimney repairs

   Brick and stone veneer

   Foundation repairs

   Waterproofing

   Outdoor kitchens and pizza ovens

   Commercial and residential projects


We use top-notch materials to ensure that our projects withstand time and weather.
